Hard to believe it’s already been 1 year since taking off the uniform…

Looking back on these experiences, I am grateful to have served with the best group of people on the planet — and would no doubt do it again given the opportunity. 🫡

For those of you that are still serving, and making up for my slack — thank you.  Even though you might not see it now, I promise that you will look back on these days with a heavy heart 🇺🇸

For my military friends — if you haven’t heard of this app, you need to check it out!  Think AirBNB — but for military! 👊 

Designed by one of my C-17 Pilot friends in Charleston…. It’s pretty dang cool! 

And no… I’m not getting paid for this lol.  Just helping out a bro that has a great idea! 

To help spread awareness, my guy at 
@crewdogsapp is doing an exclusive merch giveaway with shirts and stickers to share their mission to help the military community stick together and find places to stay.

Who can claim their shirt? Veterans, Active, Reservists, Spouses, and Families. 

How to claim your shirt:

Step 1 Follow @crewdogsapp
Step 2 Tag 3 military friends in the comments
Step 3 Repost the giveaway 
Wait for a DM!

*Free shipping until midnight EST 10/27/2023. After that, you pay shipping. 
 
@crewdogsapp is the new travel app for the military community. It’s like an Airbnb and Furnished finder app exclusively for military. It lets us share Rooms and Rentals with each other.

Host a place yourself, or share with a military rental owner who would prefer to host the military community!

It’s pretty AWESOME when you find out that one of your friends you went to Air Force Pilot training with over 20 years ago — owns a winery in Argentina! 🤯 

His name is Zane, and he owns a small company called Vinuv.  He flew C-5s for the AF…. And is currently flying the 757 & 767 for Delta. 

I have no idea where he finds the time to make it work, but his passion for wine and running a business constantly has he and his wife Mindy bouncing back and forth between the US and the Uco Valley of Mendoza, Argentina…

If you’re a wine fan, check out his lineup on the website (link in bio)…. And give him a shot to win your business.  I promise you won’t be disappointed!

Fantastic wine, great prices, and Veteran owned & operated — you won’t find a better setup to support one of our own. 

Use the discount code “Scott10” at checkout to take 10% off your order, and tell him that I sent ya — and that C17s and A320s rule the day 😉
